zb2PL1.content:
After many approaches and proposals, and due to the fact that the sustainability of the project is an important pillar for Beefy Sharks, the following was established:

  • The BSC token is established as a deflationary token, which can be reviewed in the section The burning system.

  • It has been established that 70% of the funds acquired from the purchase and sale of the NFT Beefy Sharks collection will go to the Liquidity Pool to add value to the BSC token, and because it is a deflationary token, as the price of the token increases as the tokens are burned, rest assured that 80% of the proceeds from the Beefy Sharks Collection will go to the liquidity pool. will go to the liquidity fund, for that the addresses of both the BSC Token, the NFT collection, and the BSC Token burning address will be made public in the HOME page of the Web page and in the WHITEPAPER.

  • Once all NFTs have been sold the creator will receive 2.5% for each purchase and sale of Beefy Sharks NFTs, of which 100% of the 2.5% received will go to the liquidity fund.

  • We ensure that Beefy Sharks NFT Holders, who benefit from the 10% drop of the BSC tokens, can keep them for future profitability.

THE WHITEPAPER IS AN ISSUED DOCUMENT THAT MAY BE MODIFIED IF THERE IS INPUT FROM INVESTORS AND THE COMMUNITY TO IMPROVE IT.

ztGn3i.content:
The burning system works as follows, 0.1% of each transaction will go to the public burning wallet which can be followed from BSC Scan, when 1% of the total supply in the burning wallet is reached, it will start with the burn the BSC and the cycle will continue in the same way, when the total supply of tokens decreases by 13%, the percentage of tokens that will go to the burn wallet will be decreased to 0.08%, when the total supply decreases by 25% the percentage will be close to 0.06%, and so on until reaching very small amounts and then 0.

keep in mind that the system may be subject to change and suggestions for improvement from the community.
